tch pallets to specific orders when they have information right at their fingertips even during the cooling process the it solution enables quality checkers to track product temperatures during the process and notify workers when it is complete it does not stop there as transportation is another roadblock during this stage fresh produce can remain unmonitored but not anymore when intelligent tracking systems are in place to ensure critical monitoring and coordination remote visibility powered by technology allows higher visibility of the product in various stages to help buyers or dealers accept or reject a product even before it is shipped or before it reaches the end point sellers can use technology to find other buyers and divert the produce instead of having to discard it  food safety management systems even take care of visual inspection of fresh produce to check freshness at all stages not just at the last stage one way this can prove helpful reduce waste and improve transparency is that sellers can then route such products according to various stages of freshness to nearest points of sale or consumption  typically logistics of fresh produce movement starts with harvesting and the steps involve cut to cool precooling staging shipping transit wholesale distribution and end point that may be retail or hotel or food processing an intelligent well thought out and implement software solution factors in all these stages and ensures greater transparency for all those involved not only to be better informed but to handle challenges peculiar to each stage waste that is currently in billions of dollars could reduce to a fraction of the amount transparency powered by software leads to greater collaboration and better coordination resulting in reduced waste food is consumed not discarded  the comprehensive solution covers all aspects in a modular form including pallet level tracking precooling stage pallet routing intransit monitoring freshness quality management and remote visibility a smartphone and internet connection is all it takes for everyone to share and collaborate on best food produce handling techniques in an open transparent and meaningful way  resources httpecoarkusablogspotinecoarkoverviewofhowtechnologyhtml   comments sign inrecent site activityreport abuseprint pagepowered by google sites produce management will be a thing of the past and heres why  ecoark holdings inc ecoark holdings incsearch this site home things to avoid in restaurant food safety regulations ideas to organize your own food logisticsecoark holdings inc to acquire labs cloud and mobile software developer to support zest labs in increasing supply chain efficienciesecoark holdings inc to rebrand its fresh produce subsidiary as zest labsecoark an overview of how technology improves transparencymagnolia solar uses nanotechnology to improve the efficiency of solar cells altenergymagproduce management will be a thing of the past and heres whysimple guidance for you in food safety planthe supply side trash can supplier to walmart us works to vertically integrate business modelwhy is everyone talking about temperature monitoring systemwhy is everyone talking about temperature monitoring systemsitemap produce management will be a thing of the past and heres why product management refers to the practices of management skills functioning in the production it is also term as strategies practices directing organizing and controlling the production process production management is recognizing as the point of starting and ending where individual cannot isolate in an establishment reason behind this is the connection among several functional segments of trades which are industrial finance marketing relation policies etcinstead management of production is not based upon financial personnel and marketing management because of whom it is much complicated to determine a sole particular produce management definition the advancement of industrial system of production is